Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍司 快躲開！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-劍司！\N-近藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼穹 - 天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:01:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是「痛楚」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異界體！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.71,0:02:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經下定決心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異界體 我就告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所教你的戰鬥方法的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是消耗戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要忍受痛楚的戰法！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是戰鬥的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是存在的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是面對死亡的恐懼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異界體！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要留在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要留在這裡啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的攻擊出現停滯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類軍陸續突破防衛線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進！別放過這個機會！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘可能不斷前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要像是這樣變成這座島就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會擁抱住你們大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是媽媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我要和龍宮島合而為一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回歸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們回歸虛無吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快散開！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:05:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要感謝自己還活著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是存在於這裡的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異界體…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…C地點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠見 使用縛狼刃索
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:06:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是能讓人類跟異界體共存的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太多了吧 會超載的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 大部分都正傳送到別處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍宮島？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北極傳來資料了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾維斯的所有伺服器及兀爾德之泉已自動接收
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是龐大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠超過之前接收的資料量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎他們已經抵達了紅音的意志跟希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路線淨空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有系統正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導航系統正重新接收目標周邊的相關情報
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁紅音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經告訴絕望的我們 要我們活下去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士…就在裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會…讓你們進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始進行核心的再同步作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過禁止通行了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你們搶走的東西還給我們吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…就是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:08:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵方星核的騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎他…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把敵人的意識同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「接受」也是一種力量喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 你在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吧 就在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…還在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎？你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為同化的關係 肉體的同化現象復發了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要接受治療一定會康復的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到島上吧 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核…開始行動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正前方出現敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的同化開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎麼會這樣…\N-乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的星核正想和天空連繫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它想要和大氣層外的異界體一起覆蓋住整個地球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化Mark VII武器攻擊它！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扳機由真矢來按
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將Mark Zein的能量用最大的功率釋放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會只有一次而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多的話一騎的身體無法負荷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對它們來說 那或許是唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 也不是最後的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個星核也跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了闡述生與死、存在與虛無是表裡合一不斷延續的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會誕生在這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬 妳回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到另一個星核的身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:14:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異界體…全都往下掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溝口先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認法夫那部隊所有駕駛員平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦到了 他們辦到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地底…起風了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心和島合而為一了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就可以回去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Nicht！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核用自己的死亡賦予異界體成為了個體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去會拖累所有的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠見！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 遠見！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎！一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來！同步直接連結還沒中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要少了任何一人 同步連結就沒有作用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳在戰鬥之前告訴我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎…他還活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在於任何地方 存在於這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在與虛無正相互對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在於任何地方…存在於這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎…總士…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是將一切回歸虛無 來自異界體的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕在現實的世界中 我們的存在已經消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…還在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲洋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人類的宇宙艦隊以及大氣層外的異界體核心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方都燃燒殆盡而墜落了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整艘艦艇在出發之前就被摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是引擎仍然毫髮無傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將機體的構造同化 把控制權交由系統管理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起飛之後就由我來操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能飛嗎 一騎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然能飛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我陪著你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核理解生命的循環了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是乙姬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她本人是不可能再生的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那將只是複製出同樣的事物 違背了生命的本質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經是乙姬的存在轉生成為新的事物了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼她終將成長為核心 並且能夠與我們對話的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們把這座島當作希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且繼續留在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續直走就能回到島上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來還是你救了我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎 我教導異界體什麼是痛楚與存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也理解了他們的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解了存在與虛無的循環
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在與虛無的循環？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經幾乎不存在了 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到島上一起接受治療吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這麼做吧 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會到異界體那裡一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再度創造出自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道會花上多久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 你在吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士…總士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:19:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我們重逢為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VII的緊急修理完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以出動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員的精神狀態也穩定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開第七巨龍之洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那Mark VII 出動！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡等你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:02.47,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}我可以懵懂無知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:06.88,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}眺望著夢想的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:16.93,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,3000)\fs20\be1}再見了 湛藍的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:35.34,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}即使將珍貴的事物當成跳板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:41.44,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}也想摘下最高處的蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:47.55,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}失去了才察覺到值得尊崇的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:54.96,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,1800)\fs20\be1}年幼的我們總是不得要領
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:59.57,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}充盈於每一天的鎮壓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:02.76,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}使得情緒變得不安定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:08.84,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}即使受傷也祈禱能拍動羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:15.31,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}我可以懵懂無知吧 眺望著夢想的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:21.29,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,1000)\fs20\be1}再見了 湛藍的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:33.48,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}正因為保持距離 才能得知自由的份量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:39.85,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}未成熟的心甚至無法理解這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:46.08,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}現在就敢如此斷言吧 這裡就是所謂的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:51.72,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,1300)\fs20\be1}再見了 湛藍的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:02.47,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}愚かでいいのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:06.88,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}見渡す夢の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:16.93,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,3000)\an9\fs18\be1}さよなら　蒼き日々よ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:35.34,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}大切な何かを　踏み台にしてまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:41.44,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}一番高い林檎　掴みたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:47.55,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}無くしてから気付く　尊いモノ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:54.96,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1800)\an9\fs18\be1}幼い僕等は　的はずれだらけさ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:59.57,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}満ち足りた日々の制圧は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:02.76,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}情緒不安定になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:08.84,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}傷を負ってでも　羽ばたきたいと願うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:15.31,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}愚かでいいのだろう　見渡す夢の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:21.29,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an9\fs18\be1}さよなら　蒼き日々よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:33.48,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}距離をおいてこそ　自分の大きさを知る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:39.85,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}未熟な心は　それさえ分からないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:46.08,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}今なら言えるだろう　此処がそう楽園さ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:51.72,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1300)\an9\fs18\be1}さよなら　蒼き日々よ
